ssified as instrument under Storage Systems division. The 'ATS' prefix appears to mean 'Auric Trauma System'. No conflicts detected between internal and external sources. Title accurately reflects function. No brand ambiguity - clearly part of Auric system family.","proposed_recommended_action":"keep_as_is","proposed_semantic_anatomy_scope":["Multi-Anatomical"],"proposed_semantic_brand_system":"Auric","proposed_semantic_coating_default":null,"proposed_semantic_confidence":0.95,"proposed_semantic_family_group":"Auric Trauma System Accessories","proposed_semantic_implant_class":"Not Applicable - Storage Equipment","proposed_semantic_material_default":null,"proposed_semantic_parent_brand":"Auric","proposed_semantic_procedure_scope":["Trauma Surgery","Fracture Fixation"],"proposed_semantic_review_required":false,"proposed_semantic_system_type":"Storage and Inventory System","proposed_semantic_use_case_tags":["Operating Theater Storage","Implant Inventory Management","Sequential Organization","Mobile App Integration","Surgical Workflow Optimization"],"proposed_web_verification_status":"externally_enriched","semantic_anatomy_scope":["Multi-Anatomical"],"semantic_brand_system":"Auric","semantic_coating_default":null,"semantic_confidence":0.95,"semantic_conflict_codes":[],"semantic_enriched_at":"2026-03-28T09:39:03.495281+00:00","semantic_implant_class":"Not Applicable - Storage Equipment","semantic_material_default":null,"semantic_parent_brand":"Auric","semantic_review_required":false,"semantic_rule_hits":["WEB_FALLBACK_EXTERNALLY_ENRICHED"],"semantic_system_type":"Storage and Inventory System","features_list":["Bionik Gold Surface","Coated With Titanium Niobium(TiNBn) with a specialized process","Outstanding Biocompatibility","Allergy Preventive","Become Stronger after the process compared to Conventional Implants","Long term Chemical Stability","Higher wettability with Synovail Fluid when used in close vicinity of an articular surface","Reduction of iron release"],"clinical_indications":["•\nThis concept allows the Trauma Surgeons access the required implants without pre ordering them and \nin case of emergency the availability of implants makes the surgeon task easy.","6mm\n\n\n---PAGE---\n\n14\nAURIC* Plates and Screws are available with \nARMAR* High Precision Fixation instruments sets\n\n\n---PAGE---\n\n15\n\n\n---PAGE---\n\nMeril Healthcare Pvt.","5mm LPS-Reconstruction \nCombined hole Plate\nMaterial : Titanium\nThickness : 3.","5mm LPS Distal \nFemur Plate\nMaterial : Titanium\nThickness : 6.","5mm LPS Anterior-Lateral \nDistal Tibial Plate\nMaterial : Titanium\nThickness : 2."],"brochure_source_file":"Auric Brochure.pdf","brochure_intelligence_updated":true,"visual_style":"cool_surgical_blue"}}]
